name: Renee Paquette
description:
Renee Paquette

Renee is an announcer and interviewer for All Elite Wrestling, formerly Renee Young in WWE.

This is my first paid request (thank you Dave!) and it highlights and issue doing requests - I'm not all that familiar with the subject, so it's very difficult for me to see nuances and tiny details that make or break a good likeness. I think this looks great, else I wouldn't be sharing, right? No sense uploading garbage just for the sake of it, imo.

I hope you like it, I'm open to suggestions on how to improve this one.

Do you like my work? Buy me a beer!

[ SDv1.4, 4e-03, 5500 steps ]
